      ],
      "value": "Configure Trusted Issuer(s)\\nSelect one or more trusted issuers, with the default being \"self\". This pertains to Reusable ID. If configured, users who already possess KYC credentials issued by these trusted issuers in their data vault will not need to repeat the KYC steps in the widget. They can simply authorize the sharing of their existing credentials with your app, streamlining user onboarding for your company and providing a smoother experience for your users. Read more here."
